issue.title: GPS Sensor SDF Tag Not Supported

content.raw:
I don't think the message you posted prevents the loading of a GPS plugin. The message is a warning, occurs in `physics/Link.cc`, and is related to populating a protobuf message with sensor information for consumption by the gazebo GUI.

How are you trying to load a GPS plugin?
